Basic Description about the Codniton

1.if-else
2.else if
3.ternary operator
4.switch

1. if-else statements

if(condtion){
    //something else
}else{
    //something else
}

2. else if statements

if(condtion 1){
    //something else
}else if (condition 2){
    //something else
}else{
    
}


3. ternary operator 

variable = conditon ? statement 1 : statement 2 ;

4. Switch statement

Switch (variable) {
    case 1 : 
            break;
    case 2 : 
            break;
    case 3 : 
            break;
    case 4 : 
            break:

    default : 
}


